{"tid":296714,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[港女廚房]蝦乾蒸蛋，乾荀片炒黑豚肉","createTime":"2017-06-24T21:00:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-27T06:51:04.000Z","uid":96525,"like":7,"dislike":62,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ec6e629413314f798d6c0affcbde3c310e0bdfc1","tid":296714,"uid":96525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T21:00:30.000Z","msg":"話說我記得之前有人屈我用貴價食材去掩飾自己唔識煮飯🤔<br />\n咁我今日就帶大家食平d<br />\n除咗主題兩樣餸 仲買咗半隻g 蒜蓉蒸秋葵<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/25/045542_58a006dc8f3720c111604bc039822fe4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F25%2F045542_58a006dc8f3720c111604bc039822fe4.jpg&h=c7eed449&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蝦乾蒸蛋好滑，蒸秋葵點辣椒豉油好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/25/045707_3928c9c19e74091117507fd8c7160d9c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F25%2F045707_3928c9c19e74091117507fd8c7160d9c.jpg&h=e347a14d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nClose up 蝦乾蒸蛋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/25/045745_b2a61ea23c83e1af4912009cdbe12d7c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F25%2F045745_b2a61ea23c83e1af4912009cdbe12d7c.jpg&h=1e8ae422&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後係乾荀片炒黑豚肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n老公食到讚不絕口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最後仲醒咗兩千蚊零用錢比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd88a7d664beadb68512c7e9a620ac0e006dd54c","tid":296714,"uid":2772,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T21:06:20.000Z","msg":"隻碗咁高身<br />\n叫燉蛋就差唔多"},{"pid":"31bec75f07c4eeb775b61f